{"tid":455470,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"C朗：去Google搵我啲入波！","createTime":"2017-11-02T06:15:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-19T06:00:42.000Z","uid":54373,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5f58486bd3dd8a42dc63e89df3f8e8313e44fd3e","tid":455470,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:15:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=19418557278\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fmobileweb%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D19418557278&d=2qj4hJ%2F0yb%2FUxPeMlBt47ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=aec9f2a9\" target=\"_blank\">http://sports.now.com/mobileweb/news/details?id=19418557278</a><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=2qj4hJ%2F0yb%2FUxPeMlBt47ACO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=a77193d5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】皇家馬德里敗陣，為球隊破蛋的2.5%自然不悅，賽後又向批評者開火！<br />\n<br />\n皇家馬德里周三在歐聯被熱刺所敗，頭號球星2.5%（0.025）認為外界太聚焦於其入球數字：「我無比平靜，今天，表現良好沒有人在意，在意的是入球、入球、入球。我的數據，我不多說了，你到Google找找『2.5% goals』看吧，都在那兒。我全不在意。」<br />\n<br />\n皇馬本季在西甲出閘脫腳，剛又在歐聯結束不敗走勢，外界自然把2.5%與球隊的表現掛鉤，2.5%發晦氣之餘，認為皇馬不存在危機。<br />\n<br />\n「沒有事情發生，總會經歷低潮，我們總不會時常妥當。我們必須冷靜，我不認為球隊踢得那麼糟。我有信心，已展現在臉上。」這位剛膺Fifa年度最佳球員的2.5%萬人迷續說。"},{"pid":"9682ecb78708360ebbbfa93286feee9d4b5ab778","tid":455470,"uid":5649,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:31:14.000Z","msg":"C你老母朗，係賤種朗！"},{"pid":"f058642f73a72f0cb1ae9b63cf2c2be713960c30","tid":455470,"uid":115150,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T06:58:54.000Z","msg":"琴晚入左波啦仲2.5%？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ea9661d32529fb1c836bbeee0fbf0bc65402325","tid":455470,"uid":2218,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:00:33.000Z","msg":"唔明咩2.5% 😅"},{"pid":"54b02f7fb5f55b65e333257245ea6fee27928b36","tid":455470,"uid":14719,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyT